---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import mockup from '~/assets/mockup-2.png'
---

<div class="overflow-hidden py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-y-16 gap-x-8 sm:gap-y-20 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="lg:pr-8 lg:pt-4">
        <div class="lg:max-w-lg">
          <h2 class="text-lg capitalize font-semibold leading-8 tracking-tight text-amber-500">Get good at fundamentals</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-light-100 sm:text-4xl">Meet our Learning HQ</p>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg tracking-wide leading-8 text-gray-300">The personalized learning section is a curated collection of learning materials that teach you the fundamentals of photography and videography. Based on your errors and preferences, the app will recommend you the best step by step guides.</p>
          <dl class="mt-10 max-w-xl space-y-8 text-base tracking-wide leading-7 text-gray-400 lg:max-w-none">
            <div class="relative pl-9">
              <dt class="inline font-semibold text-light-100">
                <span class="i-tabler-books absolute top-1 left-1 h-5 w-5 text-amber-500" />
                Designed to help you learn.
              </dt>
              <dd class="inline">It is designed to help you learn the theory and practice of photography and videography in a fun and engaging way. Choose from a variety of topics and browse through different genres.</dd>
            </div>

            <div class="relative pl-9">
              <dt class="inline font-semibold text-light-100">
                <span class="i-tabler-user absolute top-1 left-1 h-5 w-5 text-amber-500" />
                Tailored to your skill and style.
              </dt>
              <dd class="inline">The app will analyze your errors and preferences and suggest you the most relevant and effective learning materials for you. You can also customize your learning plan by selecting your own goals and interests.</dd>
            </div>

            <div class="relative pl-9">
              <dt class="inline font-semibold text-light-100">
                <span class="i-tabler-arrow-iteration absolute top-1 left-1 h-5 w-5 text-amber-500" />
                Interactive and adaptive.
              </dt>
              <dd class="inline">You can watch videos, read articles, and take quizzes to learn new concepts and skills. You can also apply what you learn by doing exercises and challenges with your phone camera.</dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </div>
      </div>
      <Image src={ mockup } class="w-3xl max-w-none saturate-120 brightness-80 sm:w-4xl md:-ml-4 lg:-ml-0" width="2432" height="1442" alt="App Learning section screenshot" />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
